{"tid":1043783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【巴拿馬文件】創科局長楊偉雄　任理大副校時設離岸公司","createTime":"2019-03-02T13:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T05:23:27.000Z","uid":47714,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fbb8d460f4e31aee77b11e2d35c936e7632201dd","tid":1043783,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:36:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/17853/巴拿馬文件-創科局長楊偉雄-任理大副校時設離岸公司\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F17853%2F%E5%B7%B4%E6%8B%BF%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%E6%A5%8A%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84-%E4%BB%BB%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%89%AF%E6%A0%A1%E6%99%82%E8%A8%AD%E9%9B%A2%E5%B2%B8%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=7270b63a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/17853/巴拿馬文件-創科局長楊偉雄-任理大副校時設離岸公司</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/85029/org/73dbf61e188179b6c477be2770214226.png/VlJJ4Z0p61UDSQUFMDF1hvbFk28jNHEr7ai_UO2ov1A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F85029%2Forg%2F73dbf61e188179b6c477be2770214226.png%2FVlJJ4Z0p61UDSQUFMDF1hvbFk28jNHEr7ai_UO2ov1A&h=14bee874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/84856/org/a97eff84af975850f46765bb1c180ab9.jpg/q2QloCzTmEIxhIxqrLJPYRZQ8k2pYtLC2ef4Otnn-Do\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F84856%2Forg%2Fa97eff84af975850f46765bb1c180ab9.jpg%2Fq2QloCzTmEIxhIxqrLJPYRZQ8k2pYtLC2ef4Otnn-Do&h=c63f3d2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現任創新及科技局局長楊偉雄於2013至2014年，擔任理工大學行政副校長時，曾處理理工大學開設離岸公司。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n根據巴拿馬文件揭示，香港理工大學曾透過轄下公司間接在英屬處女島（BVI）開設兩間公司，由時任理大財政處長香世傑擔任唯一董事，其中一間公司PearL-DigiPower更是由現任創新及科技局局長楊偉雄負責，楊當時為理大行政副校長。有校董聲稱對有關操作不知情。 楊偉雄今午透過政府新聞處回應《香港01》，指成立離岸公司是理大相關委員會通過的決定。由於他已不在理大任職，不方便透露詳情，但強調有關安排是出任副校長時的行政工作，當中並無不當。 至於理大方面，仍未有回覆查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/84902/org/26eb0dc4e88a3dcddb64834615a6e6bd.jpg/xMMfMaHrF3u-sfMQWU3QNCe0gPpUwBRD6nxxxOp8ccQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F84902%2Forg%2F26eb0dc4e88a3dcddb64834615a6e6bd.jpg%2FxMMfMaHrF3u-sfMQWU3QNCe0gPpUwBRD6nxxxOp8ccQ&h=e2096e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n理大企業在2013年5月末組成PearL-DigiPower。(ICIJ文件)<br />\n<br />\n涉事的兩間BVI公司由理大企業公司（PolyU Enterprises）全資擁有。理大企業是理大獨資擁有的一家香港公司，負責將理工大學的研究成果轉移到商業範疇應用。理大企業在2013年5月末組成PearL-DigiPower，當時楊偉雄正擔任理大企業的總裁。3周後，楊再以理大企業總裁名義簽署協議，令PearL-DigiPower可以將股票轉移到理大企業之下。除了PearL-DigiPower外，理大企業在2012年10月亦成立了另一家BVI公司PearL-Sun Wah。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/84912/org/9c67c7e025027557b970c159b2fd20f2.jpg/Iy6n8T9xghEtDV2qZSrPOsM0NHlHrrzlKcOpACnDqQA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F84912%2Forg%2F9c67c7e025027557b970c159b2fd20f2.jpg%2FIy6n8T9xghEtDV2qZSrPOsM0NHlHrrzlKcOpACnDqQA&h=156ad8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊偉雄以理大企業總裁名義簽署協議。(ICIJ文件)<br />\n<br />\n校董會稱不知情<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》引述兩名大學校董稱，校董會對此有關操作並不知情。報道引述理工大學校董朱偉志稱：「不記得知曉有兩家英屬處女島公司」，又批評大學設立這種公司「不合適」。報道又稱楊偉雄拒絕進一步回應：「（理工大學）已經給了你解釋，就相信吧，為什麼來問我？」 理工大學回覆該報道時，指設立兩家英屬處女島公司是為了「在理工大學已經沒有積極運作的公司中持有投資」，稱有關操作最符合效益。<br />\n<br />\n教育界立法會議員葉建源對事件感到難以理解，他質疑校方為何設立離岸公司操作研究成果應用，另外校方在設立公司過程中是否經過合適程序，有沒有繞過校董會，「若果成立過程好秘密，就好大問題。」他促請楊偉雄及理大管理層進一步解釋。"},{"pid":"acaea8bc2d92ce7b136201458749f21c80b1a29d","tid":1043783,"uid":4826,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:39:54.000Z","msg":"快d落去搵Steve Jobs啦"},{"pid":"155ce4bd2afe54915d995d762fd4009aeb03b125","tid":1043783,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:44:24.000Z","msg":"under the  table"},{"pid":"996cfb8234bf988a5b5f8b8e122080529bea3997","tid":1043783,"uid":53577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:47:33.000Z","msg":"嗰5百億去咗邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f9618bb0411c15b762495d7b2eddb874faab13","tid":1043783,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:11:25.000Z","msg":"500億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61feda548b204863db30ea1c6bc5a90b8fef7a67","tid":1043783,"uid":106030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11926748ff51280cafafabb66e73cd968b3e1c65","tid":1043783,"uid":62837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"其實會有咩事<br />\n唐英年 劏房波 立法會議員 全部都有<br />\n第日d傳媒收晒咪一樣隻字不提"},{"pid":"3ba9ea6989bde49b57f8bf44e57c37464c2f54f1","tid":1043783,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:23:13.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"35f939a6d5bb5ac43c0f9e653a69a400c3ee417f","tid":1043783,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"怕你香港人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a426e89d7ed4c063245eaf9343f8cbf7ccad1307","tid":1043783,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}